title: Moran Cerf
itunes:title: Moran Cerf
description:
Whitney gives us hot takes on the Johnny Depp/Amber Heard trial and interviews one of her favorite neuroscientists Moran Cerf.  They talk about communicating with dead brains, pole dancers,  and so much more.  Moran Cerf is assistant professor of business at Northwestern University.
